Contains  a project made for Operating Systems course.
Task Monitor which accesses the procfs from /proc and reads the stat file of every process and displays the data.
Run install.sh to setup the program.
Once it's done, press esc + z to run the task monitor.
While the program is running,
	->Press 'k' to kill a process
	->Press 'q' to exit
To uninstall, run uninstall.sh

 
